### 0) health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/health

### 1) create session
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "demo",
  "skills_roots": []
}

### 2) set roots
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/sessions/{{session_id}}/skills/roots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roots": [
    "<repo_root>/packages/skills-runtime-studio-mvp/backend/.skills_runtime_sdk/skills"
  ]
}

### 3) list skills
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/sessions/{{session_id}}/skills

### 4) create skill
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/studio/api/v1/sessions/{{session_id}}/skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "article-writer",
  "description": "写作技能",
  "body_markdown": "# 输出要求\n- 标题\n- 要点",
  "title": "Article Writer"
}

### 5) create run
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/sessions/{{session_id}}/runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "请调用 $[web:mvp].article-writer 输出 5 条测试建议"
}

### 6) pending approvals
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/runs/{{run_id}}/approvals/pending

### 7) decide approval
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/runs/{{run_id}}/approvals/{{approval_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decision": "approved"
}

### 8) stream events (SSE)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/runs/{{run_id}}/events/stream
